    "description": "<strong>Throw magic bombs! Destroy everything around you! Avenge your family!</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆ Hand-drawn levels that you can destroy! ◆</strong></h2>Make tunnels, destroy walls, use the terrain to your advantage! Every level contains terrain that can be destroyed with bombs.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328890/extras/a77784ffe4a6b671ddba298914a8e810.poster.avif?t=1685448039\" width=504 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328890/extras/a77784ffe4a6b671ddba298914a8e810.webm?t=1685448039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328890/extras/a77784ffe4a6b671ddba298914a8e810.mp4?t=1685448039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆ Elemental bombs with unique effects! ◆</strong></h2>There are 8 unique bomb types for the player to unlock, each with unique effects!<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong><i>Normal Bomb:</i></strong> A simple explosion. Very reliable!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328890/extras/7e39c12e6771d5fe74effe4729b6c610.avif?t=1685448039\" width=200 height=200 /></span><br></li><li> <strong><i>Electric Bomb:</i></strong> Spawns an Electric Star that zaps nearby enemies. (WARNING: Very volatile!)<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328890/extras/fedd2896a3d85838bcae31f9f094a680.avif?t=1685448039\" width=200 height=200 /></span><br></li><li> <strong><i>And more!</i></strong> (Play the game to find them all!)<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328890/extras/0e7542d1b0c0a2a666e7b28c5b433eb6.avif?t=1685448039\" width=200 height=200 /></span></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆ Interactions and reactions between bombs (and the environment)! ◆</strong></h2><br>Most bombs can react with each other or the environment to create something new!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <i>Throw an electric bomb at lava and watch it <strong>explode!</strong></i><br></li><li> <i>Make enemies shoot fireballs into an ice cloud to deal <strong>bonus damage</strong> to them!</i><br></li><li> <i>And <strong>more!</strong></i></li></ul><br>Use these combinations to your advantage!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328890/extras/17a3fa3aa7f655862c3b67fb707a498a.poster.avif?t=1685448039\" width=504 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328890/extras/17a3fa3aa7f655862c3b67fb707a498a.webm?t=1685448039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328890/extras/17a3fa3aa7f655862c3b67fb707a498a.mp4?t=1685448039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆ Defeat powerful Elemental Bosses and the Embodiment of Chaos! ◆</strong></h2><br>Become destruction itself and unleash your explosive power on the Elemental Bosses and the Chaos Mage!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328890/extras/bf3fd96c83cdacf7b9eabf83f83b30ee.poster.avif?t=1685448039\" width=504 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328890/extras/bf3fd96c83cdacf7b9eabf83f83b30ee.webm?t=1685448039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328890/extras/bf3fd96c83cdacf7b9eabf83f83b30ee.mp4?t=1685448039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328890/extras/62bf76a82c8afbdb150fe51da9d4abd6.avif?t=1685448039\" width=488 height=237 /></span><br>Project made for the B.A. in Interactive Product Design, B.F.A. in Animation and B.F.A. in Digital Design degrees of U-tad, University of Technology, Arts and Design.",
